{"TopicId":223640,"ForumId":144,"TopicTitle":"Right-click trajectory menu (timewarp to point/make maneuver window) disappears when hovered over and changes position to some far place in future orbit (or the center of Kerbol)","CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-11T20:02:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-11T20:02:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0win10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i710700k | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0rtx2060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32gb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight click trajectory menu changes position to some far place in future orbit (or the center of Kerbol, couldn\u0027t tell) when hovered on. The remaining time to clicked point stays normal and it can be clicked only in that weird position. Encountered on escape trajectory from Kerbin. Reproducible, encountered many times but not sure what are the requirements.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2024_02/right.mp4.9d7ef8294f2c3c4387cec5438e3cbb21.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221350\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogra